cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on visual recognition using deep networks and hierarchical classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of Bayesian approaches and joint learning, which are common in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The use of large datasets and experiments on image sets suggest that cs.MM (Multimedia) could also be a relevant category. Finally, the use of deep networks and joint learning also suggests that cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) could be a possible category.
